author: Robert Stevenson
message: Don't judge each day by the harvest you reap but by the seeds you plant.
title: Thought of the day

author: Andy Warhol
message: They say that time changes things, but you actually have to change them yourself.
title: Thought of the day

author: Benjamin Disraeli
message: Never apologize for showing feelings. When you do so, you apologize for the truth.
title: Thought of the day

author: Pema Chodron
message: The truth you believe and cling to makes you unavailable to hear anything new.
title: Thought of the day
